max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;" class="fr-fic fr-dib"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><br></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="4823" data-elementor-settings="[]" style="box-sizing: inherit; hyphens: manual;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-id="3a4a538" data-element_type="section" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 100%;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; display: flex; width: 1160px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; position: relative; display: flex; padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-content: flex-start; display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; width: 1140px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Bugungi kunda xotin-qizlar bandligini ta&rsquo;minlash, barcha sohalarda gender tengligiga erishish, mehnat bozorida kamsitishlarga barham berish va ish haqi tengligini ta&rsquo;minlash butun dunyoda dolzarb muammolardan biri hisoblanadi. Pandemiya ayollar bandligiga juda salbiy ta&rsquo;sir ko&lsquo;rsatdi. Xalqaro mehnat tashkiloti (<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">XMT</strong>) maʼlumotlariga koʻra,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2019-2020</strong>-yillarda ayollar bandligi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">4,2%ga</strong> kamaygan va jami&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">54 millionta</strong> ish oʻrni boy berilgan. Bu&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2020-yilda</strong> ishlaydigan ayollar soni&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2019-yildagiga</strong> nisbatan<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;13 million nafarga&nbsp;</strong>kamayganligini anglatadi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">XMT&nbsp;</strong>hisob-kitoblariga ko&lsquo;ra,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2022-yilda</strong> mehnatga layoqatli aholining mehnat bozorida ishtirok etish darajasi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">60% ni tashkil etgan bo&lsquo;lsa</strong>, bu ko&lsquo;rsatkich &nbsp;erkaklar o&lsquo;rtasida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">71,9% ni</strong>, ayollar orasida esa&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">46,6% ni tashkil qilgan</strong>. Umuman olganda, ayollarning iqtisodiy faolligi erkaklarning iqtisodiy faolligidan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1,5%</strong> kam.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Gender tengligini ta&rsquo;minlash bugun mamlakatimizda ustuvor yo&lsquo;nalishlardan biri hisoblanadi. Bu borada qabul qilingan qarorlar, xotin-qizlarning huquq va imkoniyatlarini kengaytirish, davlat boshqaruvi va umuman jamiyat hayotining barcha sohalarida ularning rolini oshirishni ko&lsquo;zda tutadi. 2030-yilga qadar O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasida gender tenglikka erishish strategiyasi, &ldquo;Xotin-qizlar va erkaklar uchun teng huquq hamda imkoniyatlar kafolatlari to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida&rdquo;gi qonun, XMTning &ldquo;Ayollarga nisbatan kamsitishning barcha shakllariga barham berish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida&rdquo;gi konvensiyaning ratifikatsiya qilinishi bunga misol bo&lsquo;la oladi. Oliy o&lsquo;quv yurtlarida ayollar uchun kvotalar oshirildi, magistratura bosqichi ayollar uchun bepul bo&lsquo;ldi, tadbirkorlik faoliyatini yo&lsquo;lga qo&lsquo;yishda turli imtiyozlar berilmoqda va hokazo.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Lekin shunga qaramay butun dunyoda bo&lsquo;lgani kabi, O&lsquo;zbekistonda ham ayollarning iqtisodiy faolligi erkaklarnikiga nisbatan past.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2021-yil</strong> yakunlariga ko&lsquo;ra, bu ko&lsquo;rsatkich ayollar orasida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">41,3% ni,</strong> erkaklar orasida esa&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">56,9% ni</strong> tashkil etdi. O&lsquo;zbekiston ayollarining mehnat bozoridagi iqtisodiy faolligi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">30 yoshdan</strong> boshlanadi. Sababi, o&#39;rtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">22,3 yoshida<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/career_woman#_ftn1" name="_ftnref1" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">[1]</strong></a> turmush quradi va undan keyin&nbsp;</strong>kamida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2 yilni&nbsp;</strong>tug&lsquo;ruq ta&rsquo;tilida o&lsquo;rkazadi. Undan so&lsquo;ng mehnat bozoriga qaytadi, lekin qisqa vaqtdan keyin ularning takroriy tug&lsquo;ruq ta&rsquo;tiliga chiqish ehtimoli yuqori. Shunday qilib, deyarli&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">30 yoshida</strong> ayollar martabaga erishish bilan shug&lsquo;ullana boshlaydi. Ayollarning tez-tez dekret ta&rsquo;tili va farzandlari salomatligi tufayli kasallik ta&rsquo;tiliga chiqishi ish beruvchilar orasida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ayollarning potentsial xodim&nbsp;</strong>sifatida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">jozibadorligini pasaytiradi.&nbsp;</strong>Erkaklarning potensial xodim sifatidagi afzalliklari shundaki, ular tug&lsquo;ruq ta&#39;tiliga chiqmaydi (qonuniy huquqi bo&#39;lsa ham), &nbsp;ishda ushlanib qolishga tayyor, ish bo&lsquo;yicha safarlarga borishda hech qanday to&lsquo;siqlar yo&lsquo;q.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">O&lsquo;zbekistonda mehnatga haq to&lsquo;lashdagi jiddiy tafovutning asosiy sabablaridan biri &ndash; bu kasb&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">segregatsiyasidir<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/career_woman#_ftn2" name="_ftnref2" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">[2]</strong></a>.</strong> Davlat statistika qoʻmitasi maʼlumotlariga koʻra, ishlaydigan ayollar erkaklarga nisbatan oʻrtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">39%</strong> kam maosh oladi. Jahon banki ekspertlarining fikricha, bu, jamiyatda hukm surayotgan qarashlar va O&lsquo;zbekistonda kasblarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">erkaklar</strong> va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ayollar uchun</strong> mo&lsquo;ljallangan kasblarga ajratilishi bilan bog&lsquo;liq<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/career_woman#_ftn3" name="_ftnref3" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[3]</a>.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">O&lsquo;zbekiston xotin-qizlarining&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">iqtisodiy faolligi pastligi</strong>, avvalo ularning uy-ro&lsquo;zg&lsquo;or ishlari va bola parvarishi bilan to&rsquo;liq band ekanligi bilan bog&lsquo;liq. O&lsquo;zbekiston ayollari vaqtining&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">22% ini</strong> uy yumushlari va bola parvarishiga sarflaydi. Bu ish haqi to&lsquo;lanmaydi mehnat hisoblanadi, erkaklar esa vaqtining 9% ini uy yumushlariga sarflaydi. Uy ishlari bilan bog&lsquo;liq katta mas&rsquo;uliyat &nbsp;o&lsquo;zbek ayollarining mansab pillapoyalaridan yuqori ko&lsquo;tarilishiga to&lsquo;sqinlik qiladi. Ta&rsquo;kidlash joizki, O&lsquo;zbekistondagi an&rsquo;analarga ko&lsquo;ra, uy ishlari va farzandlar tarbiyasi bilan shug&lsquo;ullanish ayolning asosiy vazifasi hisoblanadi.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">XMT</strong> tadqiqotiga ko&lsquo;ra, O&lsquo;zbekiston aholisining&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">80% i</strong> oilada erkakning ro&lsquo;zg&lsquo;or tebratishi, ayolning esa uy yumushlari va bolalar bilan shug&lsquo;ullanishini afzal ko&lsquo;radi. Mamlakat aholisining&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">93% i</strong> turmush o&lsquo;rtog&lsquo;i ishlamasa ham, ko&lsquo;pchilik uy yumushlarini ayol bajarishi kerak, deb hisoblaydi<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/career_woman#_ftn4" name="_ftnref4" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[4]</a>. Bunday qarashlarning barchasi jamiyatda ham, mehnat bozorida ham gender tengsizligi mavjudligidan dalolat beradi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ayollar faoliyatining asosiy yo&#39;nalishlari.</strong> O&lsquo;zbekistonda ayollar ko&lsquo;proq barqaror ish o&lsquo;rinlari va qulay sharoitlarni taklif qiladigan davlat sektorida ishlaydi. Ayollar bandligining tarmoq tuzilmasi shu bilan xarakterlanadiki, ular asosan ish haqi past va ish vaqti qisqaroq sohalarda ishlaydi. Bular ta&#39;lim, sog&lsquo;liqni saqlash kabi tarmoqlar va umuman, ijtimoiy soha<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/career_woman#_ftn5" name="_ftnref5" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[5]</a>. Erkaklar va ayollarning ish haqi o&lsquo;rtasidagi tafovut sababi ham aynan mana shu bilan bog&lsquo;liq.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1-rasmda</strong> <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2016</strong> va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2021-yillarda</strong> tarmoqlarda xotin-qizlar bandligining qiyosiy bahosi keltirilgan. Maʼlumotlardan koʻrinib turibdiki, Oʻzbekistonda so&lsquo;nggi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">5 yil</strong> davomida ayollar bandlik borasidagi rejalarini oʻzgartirmagan. Aytib o&lsquo;tilganidek, o&lsquo;zbek ayollari asosan ijtimoiy soha tarmoqlarida faoliyat yuritadi va aynan mana shu sohalarda eng past ish haqi kuzatiladi. Yuqori maosh to&lsquo;lanadigan sohalarda asosan erkaklar (IT-sohasi va moliya sektori) ishlaydi. E&rsquo;tiborlisi, tahlil etilayotgan davrda IT-sohasida band bo&lsquo;lgan ayollar ulushi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3%ga</strong> oshgan. Shuningdek, qishloq xo&lsquo;jaligi, tog&lsquo;-kon sanoati va ishlab chiqarish kabi og&lsquo;ir jismoniy mehnat talab etuvchi sohalarda xotin-qizlar salmog&lsquo;ining kamayishi kuzatilmoqda.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;">1-rasm</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2016 va 2021 yillarda Iqtisodiyotda band bo&rsquo;lgan ayollarning tarmoqlar bo&rsquo;yicha taqsimlanishi (foizda)</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><img src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/image-20221125142212-1.png" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: none; height: 508px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; width: 972px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Oliy ma&rsquo;lumotga ega bo&#39;lish yuqori maosh to&lsquo;lanadigan ishlarda mehnat qilish imkonini beradi.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2020-yilda</strong> respublikaning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">25 va undan katta&nbsp;</strong>yoshdagi aholisi orasida oliy ma&rsquo;lumotli&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ayollar</strong> ulushi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">13,2% ni</strong>,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">erkaklar&nbsp;</strong>ulushi esa&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">20% ni</strong> tashkil etdi. Binobarin, yuqori maoshli ishlarga ko&lsquo;proq erkaklar jalb qilinadi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ayollar orasidagi ishsizlik.</strong> <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2021-yilda</strong> ayollar o&lsquo;rtasidagi ishsizlik darajasi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">13,3% ni</strong> (taqqoslash uchun &ndash; dunyo bo&lsquo;yicha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">6,1%</strong>) tashkil etdi. Bu erkaklar o&lsquo;rtasidagi ishsizlik darajasidan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ikki baravar</strong> yuqori.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ishsiz ayollarning asosiy qismini&nbsp;</strong>oʻrta maxsus (65,8%) va oʻrta (28,5%) ma&rsquo;lumotga ega, shuningdek, qisman oliy maʼlumotli xotin-qizlar (3,4%) tashkil etadi. Ishsiz ayollarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">44%dan</strong> ortig&lsquo;i&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">15-30 yosh&nbsp;</strong>oralig&lsquo;ida. Xotin-qizlar o&lsquo;rtasida ishsizlikning eng yuqori ko&lsquo;rsatkichi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Qashqadaryo (15,5%), Surxondaryo (15,0%)&nbsp;</strong>va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Sirdaryo (4,7%)&nbsp;</strong>viloyatlarida kuzatilmoqda. Ko&lsquo;p ayollar bola parvarishi va uy ishlari bilan bog&lsquo;liq holda uyda o&lsquo;tirishga qaror qiladi. Bu esa&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">kasbiy mahoratning yo&lsquo;qolishiga</strong> olib keladi.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2021-yilda</strong> maktabgacha ta&rsquo;lim bilan qamrab olingan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3-6 yoshli</strong> bolalar ulushi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">62% ni</strong> tashkil etgan bo&lsquo;lsa,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1-6 yoshli</strong> bolalar orasida bu ko&rsquo;rsatkich&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">30% ga</strong> ham yetmagan, ya&#39;ni, bolalarning taxminan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">40-70</strong>% i uyda onalari tomonidan tarbiyalanadi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTI mutaxassislari</strong> o&lsquo;zbekistonlik ayollarning martabasi oshishi yo&lsquo;lidagi asosiy muammolarni aniqlash maqsadida ishlaydigan ayollar o&lsquo;rtasida so&lsquo;rov o&lsquo;tkazdi. So&lsquo;rovda turli faoliyat sohalarida ishlaydigan 3<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">00 nafar ayol</strong> (<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">N=300</strong>) ishtirok etdi. So&lsquo;rov joriy yilning oktyabr oyida o&lsquo;tkazildi. Respondentlarning yoshi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">16 yoshdan 65</strong> yoshgacha, o&#39;rtacha yoshi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">36 yosh</strong>. So&lsquo;rovda oliy ma&rsquo;lumotli (<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">68%</strong>), ilmiy darajaga ega (<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">13,6</strong>%), o&lsquo;rta maxsus (<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">20,6%</strong>) va umumiy ma&rsquo;lumotli (<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">7%</strong>) ayollar ishtirok etdi. Respondentlardan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">65,8% ining</strong> <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2 va undan ortiq</strong> farzandi bor,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">25%i</strong> turmush qurmagan yoki ajrashgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">So&lsquo;rov natijalari quyidagicha bo&lsquo;ldi:</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- respondentlarning deyarli&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">88%i</strong> ayollar ishlashi kerak, deb hisoblaydi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">68,4%i</strong> erkaklarga nisbatan ayollarning martabaga erishishi ancha qiyin, deb hisoblaydi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- so&lsquo;rovda qatnashganlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">52,2%i</strong>&nbsp; turmush o&lsquo;rtog&lsquo;i ishlash uchun ruxsat berganini bildirgan;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- so&lsquo;rovda qatnashganlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">38,6%i&nbsp;</strong>martabaga erishishiga &nbsp;turmush o&lsquo;rtog&lsquo;i ruxsat bermasligini,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">34,9%i</strong> jamiyat ayollarni faqat uy bekasi sifatida qabul qilishini,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">27,9%i&nbsp;</strong>uy yumushlariga ayollar mas&#39;ulligi to&lsquo;siq bo&lsquo;layotganini aytgan bo&lsquo;lsa,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">17,3%i</strong>&nbsp; to&#39;siqlar yo&#39;qligini ta&#39;kidladi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- ayollar kuniga o&lsquo;rtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">4 soat</strong> vaqtini uy yumushlariga sarflasa, erkaklar&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">bir soatdan kam</strong> sarflashi ma&rsquo;lum bo&rsquo;ldi (so&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etgan ayollarning fikriga ko&lsquo;ra);</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- respondentlar ishlayotgan kompaniyalarda rahbar ayollarning o&lsquo;rtacha yoshi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">38,6</strong> ga teng;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- kompaniyalarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3,5%i</strong>da (asosan yuridik muassasalarida) rahbarlik lavozimlarida ayollarning yo&lsquo;qligi aniqlandi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- ayollarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">46,5%i</strong> boshqaruv qobiliyati,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">40%i</strong> faqat mashaqqatli mehnat,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">15,2%i</strong> yaxshi aloqalar ularga rahbarlik lavozimlarini egallashda yordam beradi, deb hisoblashini bildirdi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- ayollarning qariyb&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">40%i</strong> yuqori lavozimlarga, xususan, iqtisodchi, huquqshunos, moliyachi va buxgalter kabi sohalarda rahbarlik lavozimlariga tayinlashda erkaklarga afzallik beriladi, deb hisoblaydi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- ayollarning deyarli&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">55%</strong> rahbarlik lavozimlariga tayinlanayotganda jins muhim emas yoki qisman muhim, deb hisoblaydi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- farzandi yo&lsquo;q yoki bitta farzandi bor ayollarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">26,2%i</strong> farzand ko&lsquo;rish lavozim oshishiga to&lsquo;sqinlik qilmaydi, deb hisoblaydi, biroq so&lsquo;rovda qatnashganlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">58,5%i&nbsp;</strong>farzand ko&lsquo;rish qarori ularning mansab borasidagi muvaffaqiyatini vaqtincha cheklaydi, deb hisoblashini ma&rsquo;lum qildi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- ayollarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">62,4%i</strong> farzandlarini maktab va maktabgacha ta&rsquo;lim muassasasidan o&lsquo;zlari olib ketishini bildirdi, bu esa ishdan erta ketishga sabab bo&lsquo;ladi va qisman martabaga erishish yo&lsquo;lidagi to&lsquo;siqlardan biri hisoblanadi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- turmush qurgan ayollarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">26,3%i</strong> turmush o&lsquo;rtog&lsquo;i ularga ishda ushlanib qolishriga ruxsat berishini,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">25,9%i&nbsp;</strong>esa ishdan kech qaytishiga salbiy munosabatda bo&lsquo;lishini ma&rsquo;lum qildi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- ayollarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">44%i</strong> turmush o&lsquo;rtog&lsquo;i ularga xizmat safariga chiqishni taqiqlashini,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">38%i</strong> esa xizmat safariga hech qanday muammosiz jo&lsquo;natishini qayd etgan;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- so&lsquo;rovda qatnashgan ayollarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">45,7%i</strong> yuqori lavozimlarni egallashni rejalashtirayotganini bildirgan. Ularning o&lsquo;rtacha yoshi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">36 yosh</strong> va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">90%i</strong> oliy ma&rsquo;lumotli yoki ilmiy darajaga ega. Shu bilan birga, ayollarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">28%i</strong> rahbarlik lavozimlarini egallashni xohlashini ma&rsquo;lum qilgan;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&ndash; ayollarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">71,3%i</strong> ishlab topgan pulini umumiy oilaviy ehtiyojlarga sarflashini qayd etgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Shunday qilib, so&lsquo;rov quyidagi xulosalarga olib keldi:</strong></h3><ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; list-style: decimal; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;"><li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both;">Respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">88%i</strong> ayollar&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ishlashi kerak</strong>, deb hisoblaydi;</h3></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both;">Ayollar uchun martabaga erishish erkaklarga nisbatan ancha qiyin, deb hisoblashadi.</h3></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both;">Xotin-qizlar uchun martabaga erishishda jamiyatda ayolning uy bekasi bo&lsquo;lishi kerakligi va turmush o&lsquo;rtog&lsquo;irning ishlashni taqiqlashi asosiy to&lsquo;siqlardan biridir.</h3></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both;">Ayollar har kuni kamida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">4 soat vaqtini</strong> uy yumushlariga, ya&rsquo;ni haq to&lsquo;lanmaydigan ishlarga sarflaydi, erkaklar esa kuniga atigi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">bir soat</strong> vaqt sarflaydi (so&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etgan ayollarning fikriga ko&lsquo;ra);</h3></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both;">Ayol rahbarlarning o&lsquo;rtacha yoshi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">38 yosh</strong>.</h3></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both;">So&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etgan ayollarning fikriga ko&lsquo;ra rahbarlik lavozimlariga tayinlashda erkaklarga ko&lsquo;proq afzallik beriladi. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</h3></li></ol><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shuningdek,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTI mutaxassislari</strong> joriy yilning aprel oyida Farg&lsquo;ona viloyatida o&lsquo;tkazilgan so&lsquo;rovlar asosida ekonometrik model yordamida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ayollarning mehnat bozorida</strong> (ishlash va ishlamasligiga)&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ishtirok etish</strong> ehtimolini baholadi. Ma&rsquo;lumotlar bazasi faqat&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">16-65 yosh&nbsp;</strong>oralig&lsquo;idagi &nbsp;ayollar bo&lsquo;yicha ma&rsquo;lumotlarni o&lsquo;z ichiga oldi. Ushbu hisob-kitoblar uchun probit<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/career_woman#_ftn6" name="_ftnref6" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[6]</a> statistik model qo&lsquo;llanildi. Model tenglamasi quyidagicha ko&lsquo;rinishga ega:</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">P (bandlik = 1| x) = b0 + b1 ayollar + b x&#39;</strong></h3><table align="center" cellspacing="0" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; width: 1140px;"><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black; background-color: rgb(247, 202, 172); height: 33px; vertical-align: top; width: 319px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Omillar</strong></h3></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border-top: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: none; border-image: initial; background-color: rgb(247, 202, 172); height: 33px; vertical-align: top; width: 224px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Koeffisientlar</strong></h3></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border-top: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: none; border-image: initial; background-color: rgb(247, 202, 172); height: 33px; vertical-align: top; width: 236px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">P/v</strong></h3></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border-top: none; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: 1px solid black; border-image: initial; background-c