 text-align: center;">0,18</h3></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border-top: none; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: none; border-image: initial; vertical-align: top; width: 236px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;">0,031</h3></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border-top: none; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: 1px solid black; border-image: initial; background-color: rgb(247, 202, 172); vertical-align: top; width: 319px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both;">Oilaninig farovonlik darajasi</h3></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border-top: none; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: none; border-image: initial; vertical-align: top; width: 224px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;">0,18</h3></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border-top: none; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: none; border-image: initial; vertical-align: top; width: 236px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;">0,075</h3></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border-top: none; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: