font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;">- 3,02</h3></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border-top: none; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: none; border-image: initial; vertical-align: top; width: 236px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;">0,005</h3></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border-top: none; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: 1px solid black; border-image: initial; background-color: rgb(247, 202, 172); vertical-align: top; width: 319px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Kuzatuvlar soni</strong></h3></td><td colspan="2" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border-top: none; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: none; border-image: initial; vertical-align: top; width: 460px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">548</strong></h3></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ekonometrik tahlil natijalari shuni ko&lsquo;rsatdiki, ayollarning ishlash yoki ishlamaslik ehtimoliga, birinchi navbatda, ularning oilaviy holati ta&rsquo;sir qiladi. Bundan tashqari, oilaning farovonligi, ta&#39;lim darajasi, qisman ayolning yoshi ham uning iqtisodiy faolligiga ta&#39;sir qiladi. Shaharda yoki qishloqda yashashi, salomatligi, farzandlarning borligi (ma&#39;lumotlar bazasida bolalari allaqachon 16 yoshga to&#39;lgan ayollar ko&#39;p) kabi omillar statistik jihatdan ahamiyatsiz bo&lsquo;lib chiqdi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">O&lsquo;tkazilgan tahlillardan xulosa qilish mumkinki, so&lsquo;nggi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">5 yil&nbsp;</strong>ichida ayollarning martabaga erishishi, mehnat bozoridagi ishtiroki yo&lsquo;lidagi ko&lsquo;plab to&lsquo;siqlar sezilarli darajada kamaygan. Bu jarayonda hukumatning jamiyat va iqtisodiyotda gender tengligiga erishish bo&lsquo;yicha qabul qilingan qarorlari asosiy omil bo&lsquo;lmoqda. Biroq o&lsquo;zbek ayollari uchun martabaga erishish erkaklarga nisbatan ancha qiyin.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">So&lsquo;rov natijalari (ayollarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">70%i</strong>) erkaklar orasida &ldquo;ayol faqat uy ishlari va bolalar bilan shug&lsquo;ullanishi kerak&rdquo;, degan fikr mavjudligini tasdiqladi. Bu fakt ekonometrik model natijalari bilan tasdiqlandi, xususan, ayolning ishlash yoki ishlamaslik ehtimoliga, birinchi navbatda, ularning oilaviy holati ta&#39;sir qilishi ma&#39;lum bo&lsquo;ldi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTI mutaxassislari</strong> tomonidan olib borilgan tadqiqot shuni ko&lsquo;rsatdiki, o&lsquo;zbek ayoli aslida kuniga&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">12 soat</strong> ishlaydi,<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;7-8 soat</strong> ishxonada va undan keyin o&lsquo;rtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">4 soat</strong> uy ishlari bilan band.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Muhabbat Ahmedova,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">PMTI guruh rahbari</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Sharifabonu Amriddinova,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">katta ilmiy xodim</strong></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(114, 114, 114);">&nbsp;</p><hr style="box-sizing: border-box; height: 1px; background-color: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px;"><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; clear: both;"><a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/career_woman#_ftnref1" name="_ftn1" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[1]</a> Davlat statistika qo&#39;mitasi</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; clear: both;"><a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/career_woman#_ftnref2" name="_ftn2" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[2]</a> Jahon Bankining &quot;Bandlikdagi gender diskriminatsiyasi&quot; tadqiqoti.</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; clear: both;"><a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/career_woman#_ftnref3" name="_ftn3" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[3]</a> Jahon Bankining &quot;Bandlikdagi gender diskriminatsiyasi&quot; tadqiqoti.</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; clear: both;"><a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/career_woman#_ftnref4" name="_ftn4" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[4]</a> <span style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17.12px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><a href="https://xs.uz/ru/post/defitsit-dostojnogo-truda-zatragivaet-zhenschin-v-bolshej-stepeni-chem-muzhchin" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: blue; text-decoration: underline; box-shadow: none;">https://xs.uz/ru/post/defitsit-dostojnogo-truda-zatragivaet-zhenschin-v-bolshej-stepeni-chem-muzhchin</a></span></span></h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; clear: both;"><a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/career_woman#_ftnref5" name="_ftn5" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[5]</a> O&#39;zbekistonda ayollar va mehnat. Gender tengligi erishish va barcha uchun munosib mehnat sari&rdquo; XMT 2020.</h5><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; clear: both;"><a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/career_woman#_ftnref6" name="_ftn6" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[6]</a> Hodisaning yuzaga kelish ehtimolini bashorat qilish uchun foydalaniladigan statistik model</h5></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit;"><i class="bi bi-eye"></i> 1597</span></div></div></div></header></header></header></header><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></div>
